@startuml
title Activity Diagram: Scene Setup & Asset Loading

|Developer|
start
:Initialize FlowJS;

|FlowJS|
:Setup managers and camera;

|Developer|
:Load model with LOD;

|Loader|
if (LOD enabled?) then (yes)
  :Load low-poly first;
  :Display immediately;
  :Load high-poly async;
  :Register with updateManager;
else (no)
  :Load standard model;
endif

|FlowJS|
:Add to scene;

|Developer|
:Load HDRI;

|Loader|
:Apply environment;

|Developer|
:Add lights;

|FlowJS|
:Start render loop;

stop
@enduml